  "title": "Business Development Manager (Hunter, Semicon)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><u><strong>Build and maintain (Hunter)</strong></u> strong distributor partnerships across the Asia-Pacific region and globally.</li><li>Drive market growth through effective channel strategies and distributor engagement.</li><li>Execute regional marketing initiatives to boost visibility and brand presence.</li><li>Develop long-term, trusted relationships with key partners.</li><li>Identify, onboard, and nurture new distributors to expand regional coverage.</li><li>Support business development activities and contribute to strategic projects.</li><li>Handle additional tasks and responsibilities as needed.</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>1–2 years of experience in sales within the <u><strong>Semiconductor </strong></u>industry, ideally with exposure to gas delivery systems.</li><li>Self-driven, adaptable to diverse cultures, and eager to learn.</li><li>Familiarity with global markets, digital tools, and product strategy.</li><li><u><strong>Willing to travel</strong></u></li></ul><p><br /><br /></p><p>If you are interested in the position , kindly send your CVs in to jasper.soh(@)randstad.com.sg</p><p>Please include your availability, expected salary and reason for leaving your current job</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p>EA: 94C3609 / Reg: R25154228</p>",
